    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Everyone loves getting rewarded. Whether there are tasks that warrant the rewards or simply just a gift, the fact remains that rewards really do make everyone smile. <a href="https://www.coxena.com" target="_self">Coxena</a> has examined its strategy for the implementation of a reward-based system, which enacts a symbiotic relationship between the<a href="https://www.coxena.com" target="_self"> Coxena</a> community and the project.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The idea is to engage the community in a series of fun activities which, in turn, become beneficial to the community members and the ecosystem.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7"><strong>A Brief Explanation of What Airdrops Are</strong></h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Airdrops can be described as a distribution of cryptocurrency or tokens to multiple wallets owned by several individuals usually for free or after performing delegated tasks. The idea is to keep the airdropped token’s project in the minds of participants or to build a new community.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">While airdrops might not be the smartest way to garner community members, it is expedient and, more often than not, serves the purpose.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7"><strong>The Coxena Airdop Model</strong></h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><a href="https://www.coxena.com" target="_self">Coxena</a> will make use of an airdrop bot on telegram that will be responsible for allocating, verifying, and collating tasks meted to the community. These tasks consist of activities across <a href="https://www.coxena.com" target="_self">Coxena</a><strong>’s</strong> social platforms, e.g, liking the posts on<strong> </strong><a href="https://www.coxena.com" target="_self">Coxena</a><strong>’s </strong>Twitter handle, joining the Telegram group and channel, following the official Medium page, and claps on the Medium page. Community members, through the bot, will be able to accrue <strong>COX, </strong>the official token of the<strong> </strong><a href="https://www.coxena.com" target="_self">Coxena</a> ecosystem.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The rewards are broken into stages, with the first totaling 500 <strong>COX</strong>. This is obtained from joining the airdrop through the airdrop bot, and performing very simple tasks. It is important to note that users will be required to solve <strong>captcha</strong> in order to eliminate bots from compromising the flow of the trend.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;"><strong>It should be noted there is a total of 2M COX available in the airdrop pool. Thus, participating in the three phases of the airdrop increases the chances of the participants getting rewarded as we want active participants only.</strong></p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7"><strong>Referral Reward</strong></h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The second stage allows users or community members to earn <strong>COX</strong> tokens through referring the campaign to their friends, family, and strangers. The reward for this task is 100<strong>COX</strong>. It is also important to note that 1<strong>COX</strong> is equivalent to 0.01$ (at the presale price). Users or community members will get a referral link to be used in tracking and convincing.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">The process for inviting, commenting, and performing mandatory activities through the registration comes next. Users who satisfy all laid down procedures are expected to submit their details as proofs to ensure that tasks were carried out to the latter. At this juncture, eligible community members will receive the rewards directly to their respective wallets.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
